Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.26,0:00:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要拯救世界的所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱离走向毁灭的大崩落危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不断旅行的里德，法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.11,0:00:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.21,0:00:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在旅途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.31,0:00:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停留的海上都市・贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.54,0:00:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满了许多的迷团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在地下的“奈雷特福音”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.99,0:00:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有等待里德他们的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又将会如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…故事已渐入佳境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.60,0:00:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长距离晶灵炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.90,0:00:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威力实在太惊人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.24,0:00:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好…首领她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.50,0:00:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算要开始攻击王都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.81,0:00:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.64,0:00:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第13话  各奔前程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前制裁之楔正朝着王都移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.96,0:01:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好进入长距离晶灵炮的射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.86,0:01:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说当它越过这片海洋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.33,0:01:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抵达大陆上空的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.03,0:01:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能对王都进行直接攻击了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.97,0:01:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.61,0:01:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办，里德？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.64,0:01:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲入制裁之楔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.22,0:01:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久就能实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.62,0:01:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的野心就能够实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.53,0:01:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基鲁  拜…拜托你开稳一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.87,0:01:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此，但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.22,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁沙  不好意思麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多人巴鲁沙会撑不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  巴鲁沙冲过去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来怎么办，里德？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.71,0:02:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去艾克丝西亚那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.51,0:02:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把大晶灵抢回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮你们去找艾克丝西亚本体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.11,0:02:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.48,0:02:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，行动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面右转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.63,0:02:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.20,0:02:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来她不想让我们太简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能到她那里去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.35,0:03:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害哦~  往这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边右转！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直走！  左转！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.25,0:03:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再左转！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面往直走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直走到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.20,0:03:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里恐怕就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这好像是巨型晶灵仪表板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来早就坏掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不必担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？  你躲在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德  前面  她在前面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的就能达成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是…艾克丝西亚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.72,0:04:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像比我还小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚  把大晶灵还给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴…  咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德  你看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.12,0:04:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我跟我的同胞合而为一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大晶灵…如果你们抢得回去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就试试看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,散开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.01,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个退到后面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.98,0:05:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜妮玛！可莉娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.99,0:05:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.34,0:05:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.34,0:05:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.34,0:05:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普拉提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮  住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.07,0:06:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办才好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时刻终于来到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长距离晶灵炮  准备发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是做这种事的时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚和赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双方正面临一场危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有大晶灵的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望此时能拥有力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有能够拯救大家的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒艾克丝西亚大人的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止制裁之楔的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量…  力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到力量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  不可以！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.19,0:07:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.33,0:07:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.15,0:08:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.19,0:08:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…艾克丝西亚吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.71,0:08:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有发射？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.83,0:08:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.09,0:08:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晶灵炮呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.90,0:08:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好大家都没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.83,0:08:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她恐怕就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.14,0:09:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成那女孩就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.01,0:09:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，她就是艾克丝西亚的本体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了  别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.85,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这个时候，你会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.45,0:09:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要破坏我们的野心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.20,0:09:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且居然是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.67,0:09:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于战争已经是过去的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我脱离你的意义又何在呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.28,0:09:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个意义老早就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信你应该也有察觉到才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.92,0:09:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之楔就被转用为他途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.86,0:10:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却被憎恨利用过度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像身为你父母的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.07,0:10:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全被封印起来一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而漫长的岁月  也改变了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只留下憎恨而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.86,0:10:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.76,0:10:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要保护赛克斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚  希望你能听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是分什么赛克斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.90,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是茵费利亚的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.90,0:10:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大崩落就快…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.84,0:10:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚和赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.77,0:10:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相撞的现象…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.11,0:10:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大崩落在不久的将来一定会发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.38,0:10:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是为了阻止这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才出来旅行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是一面收集大晶灵呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大崩落？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.78,0:10:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.17,0:11:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你的  可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能把大晶灵从那里放出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凭可莉娜的能力一定办得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.15,0:11:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心  你一定有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇~责任好重哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.99,0:11:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那身体放松吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.86,0:11:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太认真的样子一点都不像你哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.09,0:11:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.73,0:11:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大晶灵  请你们出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于可以出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.16,0:12:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身体都僵掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.63,0:12:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了  人类还真爱胡搅瞎搞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.94,0:12:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回来了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.07,0:12:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.74,0:12:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  只是有点累而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜  谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.85,0:12:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里  没什么好谢的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.90,0:12:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.17,0:12:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮・布鲁卡诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我杀害了你的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你尽量打我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.64,0:13:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到你气消为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.22,0:13:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.95,0:13:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这次的旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微学到了一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.49,0:13:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找人复仇的那种空虚感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,况且你身边的那个小不点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.93,0:13:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还救了我一命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么可莉娜・索鲁珍特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请过来发泄你的怨恨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你…并不是我真正的妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你毕竟还是我的妈妈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.85,0:13:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首领…您还是贝鲁卡纽的领主！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我们一起回贝鲁卡纽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.25,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！  首领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.06,0:13:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.49,0:13:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我们将恢复原来的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.93,0:13:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变回两千年前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个普通少女的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.96,0:13:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔・查伊贝尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂  法拉・奥尔斯达特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德・哈谢尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.67,0:14:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们毁掉这制裁之楔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你先带大家逃离这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.94,0:14:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的人退到一边去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.95,0:14:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋  算你赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  狠狠地干一场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德  你看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙不是都逃之夭夭了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.43,0:15:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是艾克丝西亚变回普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以导致它们失去控制吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.38,0:15:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好~我们上！  好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊弗力特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西尔夫！  看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.87,0:16:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.97,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又可以继续旅行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.01,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要谢谢各位大晶灵的帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.18,0:16:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了加敬语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  应该说“非常感谢”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处罚你们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用劳驾领主大人您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.87,0:16:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是代理领主而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…钉子  铁锤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.18,0:16:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人要买啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.05,0:16:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，蜜妮玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是代理领主耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.85,0:17:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉老毛病又犯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.69,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这次少了不少居民呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.69,0:17:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些追求自己梦想的新城市的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是无法阻止的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.06,0:17:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人不知何时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才会回来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.37,0:17:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过只希望艾克丝西亚大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.87,0:17:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有离开这里的人们能早日回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.97,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且成为比过去更棒的岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医…医生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老人家就别太勉强自己了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.65,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会输给那些年轻人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮，你在看什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.17,0:17:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在眺望天空而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天气好好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.44,0:18:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.34,0:18:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道里德他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.55,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到达赛雷斯提亚了没？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁晓得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…不跟里德他们一起回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.79,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.96,0:18:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.59,0:18:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实，玛萝妮你自己想跟去吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放任你们两个自己出去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.27,0:18:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.65,0:18:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于启程到赛雷斯提亚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界的人们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有曾经互相交心的朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.13,0:18:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只希望你们的旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.07,0:18:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只希望你们的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满了光明希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信你们而继续活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在充满希望的明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.29,0:19:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挚爱的人们启程之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此将这首诗…送给你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.66,0:19:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是这种感觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.83,0:19:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  行得通行得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.80,0:19:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮，那不是法拉的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.87,0:19:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德  法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.17,0:19:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的未来…全交给你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.18,0:19:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…故事将进入未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.74,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（全剧终）
